  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a grill or grill pan to medium-high heat.",
    "Form the ground beef into 4 patties.",
    "Season the patties with salt and pepper.",
    "Brush the grill or grill pan with olive oil.",
    "Grill the patties for 4-5 minutes per side, or until cooked to your desired level of doneness.",
    "Meanwhile, toast the brioche buns on the grill or in a toaster.",
    "Cook the bacon slices in a pan over medium heat until crispy.",
    "Assemble the burgers by spreading mayonnaise on the bottom bun, followed by a lettuce leaf, a beef patty, a few slices of bacon, a slice of cheese, a few slices of pickle, and finally the top bun.",
